Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.28,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}To a land so far away.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.66,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}I feel the distance in-between.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.22,0:07:09.26,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}A fragment of the world that used to be.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.64,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Speaking through the river stream.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.90,0:07:17.20,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Calling to me, luring me down.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.36,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Though I know just what I am.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.36,0:07:25.36,udrgrd rvr,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Who I could be is the mystery to solve.
